'''瑙拉'''<ref>{{Cite web|title=2018出口奖前瞻之新南威尔士州：将科技融合时尚 (2018-11) - Austrade|url=https://www.austrade.gov.au/local-sites/china/buy-from-australia/case-studies/nsw-export-award-2018|accessdate=2021-01-01|last=Commission|first=Australian Trade and Investment|work=www.austrade.gov.au}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=新州Shoalhaven动物园一管理员遭两狮子袭击|url=https://www.sbs.com.au/language/mandarin/zh-hans/nsw-shoalhaven-zoo-lion-attacked-a-zookeeper|accessdate=2020-12-30|work=SBS Your Language|language=zh-hans}}</ref>（英文：Nowra），也译作'''诺拉'''<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.destinationnsw.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/fs-great-drives-nsw-mandarin.pdf |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-01-09 |archive-date=2015-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150321184029/http://www.destinationnsw.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/fs-great-drives-nsw-mandarin.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.investregional.nsw.gov.au/assets/_generated_pdfs/illawarra-shoalhaven-zh-cn-199.pdf |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-01-09 |archive-date=2021-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111094822/https://www.investregional.nsw.gov.au/assets/_generated_pdfs/illawarra-shoalhaven-zh-cn-199.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是个位於[[悉尼|雪梨]]以南偏西117公里處(行车距离160公里)的市(官方定义其为“city”)<ref>{{Cite web|title=Nowra-Bomaderry {{!}} New South Wales, Australia|url=https://www.britannica.com/place/Nowra-Bomaderry|accessdate=2021-01-03|work=Encyclopedia Britannica|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119085001/https://www.britannica.com/place/Nowra-Bomaderry|dead-url=no}}</ref>，人口约二万五千<ref>{{Cite web|title=Nowra {{!}} Aboriginal Housing Office|url=https://www.aho.nsw.gov.au/applicants/era/about/chapters/locations/nowra|accessdate=2021-01-02|work=www.aho.nsw.gov.au|archive-date=2021-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210403105713/https://www.aho.nsw.gov.au/applicants/era/about/chapters/locations/nowra|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

它位處[[新南威爾斯州|新南威爾斯州]]的農業地帶，经济活动以乳業和旅游业為主；附近有州立森林園區，因此在雪梨和[[坎培拉|坎培拉]]市民眼中，是休閒和渡假的好去处。镇中心的公园“Marriott Park”设有多种设施，适用于各样活动<ref>{{Cite web|title=Marriott Park|url=https://www.shoalhaven.nsw.gov.au/For-Residents/Community-Facilities/Marriott-Park|accessdate=2021-01-02|work=www.shoalhaven.nsw.gov.au|language=en-AU|archive-date=2021-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210806044225/https://www.shoalhaven.nsw.gov.au/For-Residents/Community-Facilities/Marriott-Park|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

词语“Nowra”源於澳大利亞原住民語''nou-woo-ro''，意為「黑鸚鵡」或「紮營地」<ref name="SMH">"[http://www.smh.com.au/news/New-South-Wales/Nowra/2005/02/17/1108500198352.html Travel: Nowra] {{Wayback|url=http://www.smh.com.au/news/New-South-Wales/Nowra/2005/02/17/1108500198352.html |date=20080906142616 }}", ''[[Sydney_Morning_Herald|Sydney Morning Herald]]'', [[8_February|8 February]] 2004. Retrieved on 2007-04-26.</ref>。

==地理及行政==
瑙拉乃行政区域[[肖尔黑文市|肖尔黑文市]]之商务核心。它位处[[肖尔黑文河|肖尔黑文河]]南岸<ref>{{Cite web|title=Nowra {{!}} Shoalhaven {{!}} South Coast NSW|url=https://www.shoalhaven.com/nowra-shoalhaven-south-coast-nsw|accessdate=2021-01-02|date=2017-06-25|work=www.shoalhaven.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125074943/https://www.shoalhaven.com/nowra-shoalhaven-south-coast-nsw|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

它與该河北岸的[[博马德里|博马德里]]镇在土地发展和经济生产等方面关系十分密切，常被合称“Nowra-Bomaderry”并一同规划处理<ref>{{Cite web|title=Planning for Growth in Nowra-Bomaderry|url=https://getinvolved.shoalhaven.nsw.gov.au/planning-for-growth-nowra-and-bomaderry|accessdate=2021-01-02|work=Get Involved Shoalhaven|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324183337/https://getinvolved.shoalhaven.nsw.gov.au/planning-for-growth-nowra-and-bomaderry|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

有数个以“Nowra”命名的其他行政区域与之相接。它们是“North Nowra('''北瑙拉''')”、“South Nowra('''南瑙拉''')”、“West Nowra('''西瑙拉''')”和“Nowra Hill('''瑙拉山''')”<ref>{{Cite web|title=General Mapping Information|url=https://www.shoalhaven.nsw.gov.au/Services/Maps-Online/General-Mapping-Information|accessdate=2021-01-03|work=www.shoalhaven.nsw.gov.au|language=en-AU|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124031832/https://www.shoalhaven.nsw.gov.au/Services/Maps-Online/General-Mapping-Information|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

